; Regression test for issue #1048: --pivot=commodity doesn't work (BZ#1048)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1048
;
; When using --pivot with a tag whose value matches a commodity name (e.g. EUR),
; and multiple postings share a common parent account, the tag value is
; incorrectly prepended to the account name (EUR:Assets instead of Assets).

2024/01/01 Groceries
    ; commodity: USD
    Expenses:Food   $50.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/02 Exchange
    ; commodity: EUR
    Assets:Savings   100 EUR @ $1.10
    Assets:Cash

test bal --pivot commodity
            $-110.00
             100 EUR  commodity
            $-110.00
             100 EUR    EUR:Assets
            $-110.00      Cash
             100 EUR      Savings
                   0    USD
             $-50.00      Assets:Cash
              $50.00      Expenses:Food
--------------------
            $-110.00
             100 EUR
end test
